Package org.dcm4che2.iod.module.pr

Class Summary
DisplayedAreaModule C.10.4 IOD for Displayed Area information.
DisplayShutterModule C.7.6.11 Shutter to opaque areas.
GraphicAnnotationModule C.10.5 Graphic annotations provide information about lines and circles displayed on the image(s).
GraphicLayerModule C.10.7 Provide the colour, z-index and other related graphical layer information.
GraphicObject Represents a part of the Graphic Annotation Module, the graphic object from C.10.5
MaskModule C.11.13 and C.7.6.10 define the mask subtraction to remove pixel information that is common between multiframe images.
OverlayActivationModule C.11.7 Define which overlays are to be displayed on different images.
OverlayPlaneModule C.9.2 Define a bitmap overlap to provide data on top of an image.
SpatialTransformationModule C.10.6 Define the spatial transformation - rotate and flip for an image.
TextObject Defines the text object sequence from C.10.5
